Subject:Re: [EVDL] Cross Country EV?

Bob  Albertson, the inventor of the Weed Eater, who lives in Alma, Wisconsin, claims to have an electric pickup truck that he  can drive from New York to San Francisco without ever buying a drop of gas or stopping to recharge the batteries.  He has a demo of the truck on his website.  Check it out.
